name: Ampal - Seven Seas Blue
description:
Custom Ampal 6 Panel Snap Back Baseball Cap

Reversed SEVEN SEAS Print Upper 
Chambray Brim 
Woven Label, Rope & Embroidery Detail 
Hawaiian Print Lining

We chose this amazing reissued 50’s print from the Hoffman Archives for the SEVEN SEAS snap back. We reversed it to give it a faded vintage look and lined it with a complimentary hawaiian print.

This is the third version of the Seven Seas snapback and we decided to add a little contrast with the premium chambray brim and button. We also respect the functionality of a trucker hat, but they always look cheap to us, so we added a single mesh panel up top to keep it cool in the sun.

Best enjoyed with a mai tai in one hand and sand between your toes.

name: I Love Ugly- Aloha light
description:
Our five panel caps show a true appreciation for style and design. The Aloha Light Cap is made from unique fabric that has been carefully sourced from the far east, giving it it's own individuality and character. It's an everyday wear which fits well with all of our other garments.

Each cap has been triple fused to ensure quality and the perfect I Love Ugly shape. The materials are hand sourced from Beijing and Tokyo. Features include unique vertical brass signature eyelets; adding that special I Love Ugly twist, which is backed with a genuine custom stitched leather strap and buckle.

The Fabric for the Aloha cap series was inspired by our last seasons palm tree shirt. Sourcing a similar fabric for this hat seemed like an obvious move, and if we say so ourselves, it looks pretty dope.
